<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Quitclaim Deed - {{ county }} County, California</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            font-size: 12pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .document-container {
            max-width: 8.5in;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0.75in;
        }
        .header-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .document-title {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .recording-info {
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }
        .recording-grid {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .recording-row {
            display: table-row;
        }
        .recording-cell {
            display: table-cell;
            padding: 5px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .recording-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 30%;
        }
        .risk-warning {
            border: 3px solid #ff0000;
            background-color: #fff5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .risk-warning-title {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #cc0000;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .risk-warning-text {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #cc0000;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .parties-section {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .parties-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .legal-description {
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border-left: 4px solid #333;
        }
        .legal-description-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .quitclaim-clause {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: justify;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #fffacd;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .no-warranty-section {
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            border: 2px solid #4169e1;
        }
        .no-warranty-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4169e1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .no-warranty-list {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .execution-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin: 40px 0;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            width: 300px;
            height: 40px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 20px 10px 0;
        }
        .signature-label {
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .notary-section {
            margin-top: 60px;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 20px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        .notary-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .notary-text {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .notary-signature-block {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .tax-exemption {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border: 1px solid #999;
        }
        .validation-warnings {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
        }
        .warning-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #856404;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .warning-list {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #856404;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="document-container">
        <!-- Recording Information Block -->
        <div class="recording-info">
            <div class="recording-grid">
                <div class="recording-row">
                    <div class="recording-cell recording-label">Requested by:</div>
                    <div class="recording-cell">{{ requested_by }}</div>
                </div>
                {% if apn %}
                <div class="recording-row">
                    <div class="recording-cell recording-label">APN:</div>
                    <div class="recording-cell">{{ apn }}</div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="recording-row">
                    <div class="recording-cell recording-label">Mail to:</div>
                    <div class="recording-cell">
                        {% if return_to.name %}{{ return_to.name }}<br>{% endif %}
                        {% if return_to.address %}{{ return_to.address | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}{% endif %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Document Title -->
        <div class="header-section">
            <div class="document-title">Quitclaim Deed</div>
            <div>{{ county }} County, California</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Risk Warning Section -->
        <div class="risk-warning">
            <div class="risk-warning-title">⚠️ Important Notice ⚠️</div>
            <div class="risk-warning-text">
                THIS IS A QUITCLAIM DEED<br>
                NO WARRANTIES OR GUARANTEES OF TITLE ARE PROVIDED<br>
                BUYER ASSUMES ALL RISKS
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tax Exemption Section -->
        {% if dtt_exempt %}
        <div class="tax-exemption">
            <strong>Documentary Transfer Tax:</strong> EXEMPT<br>
            <strong>Reason:</strong> {{ exemption_reason }}
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- Validation Warnings -->
        {% if validation_warnings %}
        <div class="validation-warnings">
            <div class="warning-title">⚠️ Important Considerations:</div>
            <ul class="warning-list">
                {% for warning in validation_warnings %}
                <li>{{ warning }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- Parties Section -->
        <div class="parties-section">
            <div class="parties-title">Parties to this Conveyance</div>
            
            <p><strong>GRANTOR(S):</strong></p>
            <p>{{ grantors_text }}</p>
            
            <p><strong>GRANTEE(S):</strong></p>
            <p>{{ grantees_text }}</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quitclaim Clause -->
        <div class="quitclaim-clause">
            <p>The above-named Grantor(s) hereby REMISE, RELEASE, and forever QUITCLAIM to the above-named Grantee(s), 
            all right, title, and interest which the Grantor(s) now have or may hereafter acquire in and to the following 
            described real property situated in {{ county }} County, California:</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Legal Description -->
        <div class="legal-description">
            <div class="legal-description-title">Legal Description</div>
            <p>{{ legal_description }}</p>
            
            {% if apn %}
            <p><strong>Assessor's Parcel Number:</strong> {{ apn }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- No Warranty Section -->
        <div class="no-warranty-section">
            <div class="no-warranty-title">No Warranties Provided</div>
            <p><strong>By accepting this quitclaim deed, the Grantee(s) acknowledge that:</strong></p>
            <ul class="no-warranty-list">
                {% for disclosure in risk_disclosures %}
                <li>{{ disclosure }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            <p><strong>The Grantor(s) make no representations regarding:</strong></p>
            <ul class="no-warranty-list">
                <li>The validity or extent of title to the property</li>
                <li>The existence or absence of liens, encumbrances, or other title defects</li>
                <li>The legal description accuracy or completeness</li>
                <li>Compliance with zoning, building codes, or other regulations</li>
                <li>The condition or habitability of any improvements on the property</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Execution Section -->
        <div class="execution-section">
            <p><strong>TO HAVE AND TO HOLD</strong> the above described property unto the said Grantee(s), 
            and to the heirs and assigns of said Grantee(s) forever.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Dated:</strong> {{ execution_date }}</p>
            
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Grantor</div>
                </div>
                
                <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Grantor (if applicable)</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Notary Section -->
        <div class="notary-section">
            <div class="notary-title">Notary Acknowledgment</div>
            
            <div class="notary-text">
                <p>State of California</p>
                <p>County of {{ county }}</p>
                
                <p>On ________________, before me, ________________________________,
                personally appeared ________________________________,
                who proved to me on the basis of satisfactory evidence to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are 
                subscribed to the within instrument and acknowledged to me that he/she/they executed the same in 
                his/her/their authorized capacity, and that by his/her/their signature(s) on the instrument the 
                person(s), or the entity upon behalf of which the person(s) acted, executed the instrument.</p>
                
                <p>I certify under PENALTY OF PERJURY under the laws of the State of California that the foregoing 
                paragraph is true and correct.</p>
                
                <p>WITNESS my hand and official seal.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="notary-signature-block">
                <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Signature of Notary Public</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Final Risk Notice -->
        <div class="risk-warning" style="margin-top: 40px;">
            <div class="risk-warning-title">Final Notice to Grantee(s)</div>
            <div class="risk-warning-text">
                YOU ARE STRONGLY ADVISED TO OBTAIN TITLE INSURANCE<br>
                AND CONSULT WITH A QUALIFIED ATTORNEY<br>
                BEFORE ACCEPTING THIS QUITCLAIM DEED
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Document Metadata -->
        <div style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 8pt; color: #999; text-align: center;">
            Generated: {{ generated_at }} | Document Type: {{ document_type }} | Version: {{ generator_version }}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


